prompts.prompt: In a galaxy far, far away, Nikhil the elephant, along with his friends dog, cat, and horse, embarked on a space adventure. They found themselves on a planet with purple skies and glittering stars, surrounded by strange alien creatures.

As they explored the alien planet, they came across a giant spaceship that had crash-landed. Nikhil and his friends decided to investigate, hoping to find any survivors. Inside the spaceship, they discovered a group of friendly aliens who were stranded and needed help repairing their ship.

Working together, Nikhil and his friends used their unique strengths to fix the spaceship and send the aliens safely back home. The aliens thanked them for their kindness and rewarded them with a magical crystal that granted them the ability to travel through space and time. With their new gift, Nikhil and his friends set off on more exciting adventures across the universe.
